Name: Good Boy!
About the game: The game 'Good boy' is an arcade game. Your character is the dog 'good boy'. The objective of the game is to get to the owner what she has lost. A good boy will face complex obstacles: garbage cans, fire hydrants, lasers, smart missiles and much more. Features: - 3 difficult levels that need to go through a certain time with a limited amount of money on lives - 3 bosses - leaders of world nuclear powers - 5 lives and a timer -Incredibly simple interface -Many humor Good luck!
